15
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,030
Don't be silly.

16
00:02:40,550 --> 00:02:41,110
Come on,

17
00:02:41,110 --> 00:02:42,750
let's finish the medicine first,

18
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:43,440
okay?

19
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,320
I...

20
