Drink.

27
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,880
Don't spit it out.

28
00:03:29,270 --> 00:03:31,110
Drink up.

29
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,390
I'll kill you, you bastard!

30
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,640
If you kill him, you'll get caught.

31
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,230
Is that worth it?

32
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:34,880
It is.

33
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:37,790
I have to avenge my sister.

34
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,920
The county yamen
will deal with his crimes.

35
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,000
You have to believe that

36
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,720
Magistrate Han will punish the evil.

37
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:45,830
I am guilty.

38
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:46,920
I admit it.

39
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,760
But he's the ringleader.

40
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,320
He forced me to do all this.

41
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,390
How dare you?

42
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,200
Your Honor, please.

43
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,110
This is all his one-sided story.

44
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,790
He's like a rabid dog,

45
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:00,040
accusing me to get himself off.

46
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,880
He's not credible.

47
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:02,320
Your Honor,

48
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,000
I have a copy of his prescription
as proof.

49
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:04,950
Present it.

50
00:05:05,110 --> 00:05:05,830
Yes.

51
