Fortunately, I kept one.

54
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,480
Otherwise, I'd be framed.

55
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,510
He can forge letters and the will,

56
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,670
Of course
he can forge this prescription too.

57
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,230
Your Honor,

58
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,040
it's not forged.

59
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,720
Hua Miao

60
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:50,440
is White Fan,
the second-in-command of the White Ant.

61
00:05:51,550 --> 00:05:52,320
Didn't you capture

62
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,350
two men of the White Fan?

63
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,880
You can bring them for confrontation.

64
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,600
It's self-evident.

65
00:05:57,790 --> 00:05:58,720
No need.

66
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,830
Even if I am the White Fan,

67
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:00,670
so what?

68
00:06:00,790 --> 00:06:02,350
I haven't killed anyone
or kidnapped anyone.

69
00:06:02,350 --> 00:06:03,320
