70
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:04,270
It's not like that.

71
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,320
It's not like that at all.

72
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,720
Your Honor,

73
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,510
