74
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,480
it's the person who committed the crime,

75
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,070
not the knife.

76
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,830
I...I am just like the knife.

77
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,550
Please spare my life.

78
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,600
Your Honor, please spare my life.

79
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,230
Right.

80
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,760
For the sake of the baby.

81
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,760
I have an unborn child.

82
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:23,670
I can't let my child

83
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:24,670
be born without a father.

84
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,720
Our family has one descendant
for three generations in a row.

85
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,760
After I married into the Qiao family,

86
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,320
I never thought

87
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,830
I'd have a child with the surname He.

88
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,600
But now I do.

89
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,270
I can't die.

90
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,670
I'm gonna give him a name

91
00:06:33,670 --> 00:06:34,600
with the surname He.

92
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,270
I'll teach him to read and write.

93
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,200
Right, Qiu can testify.

94
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,830
Qiu,

95
