tell the magistrate

96
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,950
that the prescription
was written by Hua Miao.

97
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:45,950
It's all his ideas.

98
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:46,950
Tell him.

99
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,270
Is what he said true?

100
