I don't know.

101
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,110
I wasn't involved.

102
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:53,270
I don't know

103
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,790
about the prescription you said.

104
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,440
As far as I know,

105
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:59,720
Hua Miao is just
the doctor of the Qiao family.

106
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,350
He doesn't have
any malicious intentions.

107
00:07:01,550 --> 00:07:03,550
He wouldn't come up with bad ideas.

108
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,720
Qiu,

109
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,390
even if you don't think of me,

110
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,950
think of our child!

111
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:09,230
No.

112
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:09,510
He can't...

113
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,920
It's not your baby.

114
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,640
His surname is not He.

115
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,920
Whose child is this?

116
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,550
It's yours.

117
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,480
You've been lying to me.

118
00:07:45,550 --> 00:07:46,760
How did I lie  to you?

119
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:49,230
Did I force you to like Qiu?

120
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:51,160
It was you who get obsessed with Qiu

121
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,670
at your first sight.

122
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:54,160
I couldn't stop you.

123
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:57,040
I felt pity for you,

124
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,270
so I let it happen.

125
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:00,070
If you had ever acted like a real man,

126
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:01,160
this child's surname would be He.

127
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,390
But are you a man?

128
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,510
He Shenwei,

129
00:08:05,350 --> 00:08:06,390
look at yourself.

130
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,320
You stupid fool.

131
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,880
You've had a bad character
since childhood.

132
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,670
Do you think you'll get rich

133
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:13,000
and achieve greatness

134
00:08:13,270 --> 00:08:14,830
by marrying into the Qiao family?

135
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:17,270
You're just a kept man,

136
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,350
with good appearance,

137
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,720
but being lecherous.

138
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:23,640
I used to flatter and pamper you,

139
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,790
thinking of you as a pig

140
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:27,790
that I would fatten up
before slaughtering.

141
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:31,040
Little did I expect
that you're not even worthy of a pig.

142
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,710
He has to be alive.

143
00:08:39,790 --> 00:08:40,520
We can't let him die.

144
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,760
I'm gonna kill you!

145
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,790
Save him.

146
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,590
Hurry up.

147
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,880
He Shenwei has been sentenced to death.

148
00:09:04,230 --> 00:09:05,710
Hua Miao can't escape punishment either.

149
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,960
Ruhui may rest in peace now.

150
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:29,320
Ruhui, come get me.

151
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,000
Come on!

152
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,790
Slow down.

153
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:37,350
Ruhui, what's this?

154
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:41,080
This is the raw material
for brewing liquor.

155
00:09:43,350 --> 00:09:44,230
Is it fun?

156
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:45,000
Yes.

157
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,080
Do you want to learn
how to brew liquor with me?

158
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,710
Yes.

159
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:49,470
Let me tell you.

160
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,200
This...

161
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,000
If your sister's spirit
is watching over from heaven,

162
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:16,350
she must want you to live well

163
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,550
and brew good liquor for her.

164
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,440
Make yourself happier,

165
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,470
and she'll be happy too,

166
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,320
right?

167
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:05,200
Do you remember now?

168
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,030
Who's the leader of the White Ant?

169
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,470
Who are the junior leaders?

170
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:10,670
Where is the den of the White Ant?

171
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,000
Gathering people to be bandits,

172
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,230
kidnapping and selling women.

173
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:20,710
Do you know that
these are serious crimes?

174
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:30,520
If you have the evidence,

175
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:32,590
just pass sentence.

176
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,440
You don't need to come

177
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,840
and interrogate me every day.

178
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:37,030
Do you really think

179
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,590
I can't sentence you to death?

180
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:42,790
No matter what,

181
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:45,000
you have to sentence me
by the laws of the Ming Dynasty.

182
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:47,320
You will suffer from your stubbornness.

183
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,590
The worst case scenario is death.

184
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,880
I'm at your disposal,

185
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:00,640
whatever you want.

186
00:12:00,710 --> 00:12:01,440
Alright.

187
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:03,110
I'll let you know.

188
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:04,760
Though your life may be spared,

189
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:05,910
the punishment will be severe.

190
00:12:12,710 --> 00:12:13,590
Get up.

191
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:15,710
What are you gonna do?

192
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,280
Let me go.

193
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,960
Leave me alone.

194
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,400
Where are you taking me?

195
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,320
Where are you taking me?

196
00:12:29,710 --> 00:12:31,000
Take him back to jail.

197
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,440
Tie him up.

198
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:46,080
Let me go!

199
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,520
Don't...

200
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,880
I confess.

201
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,640
I confess.

202
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:57,110
You really should think it through.

203
