If it weren't for the case of
the Qiao family,

204
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:00,840
the day they kidnapped Luo Shu

205
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,760
and Qiao Ruolan,

206
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:02,880
I would have eliminated them.

207
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,760
It's not as simple as you think.

208
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:05,710
Coachmen, boatmen, middlemen,
waiters and porters.

209
00:13:05,710 --> 00:13:07,110
Those are lowlifes

210
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:08,910
who always collude with each other.

211
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:10,110
If that bandit leader catches on

212
00:13:10,110 --> 00:13:10,640
and stirs up trouble...

213
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,150
I'll capture the leader.

214
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:14,710
This time,

215
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,200
I will eradicate the White Ant,

216
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,840
this poisonous tumor
that has taken root in Linfen

217
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,200
and harmed the people.

218
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,150
Muzhi, why can't you figure out

219
00:13:22,150 --> 00:13:23,150
what's truly important?

220
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:23,550
This is

221
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,350
a thankless task.

222
00:13:26,760 --> 00:13:28,670
Apart from trafficking women,

223
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:29,910
the White Ant hasn't committed
major crimes.

224
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,470
Over a decade,

225
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,760
all those magistrates have chosen to

226
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,590
coexist peacefully with it.

227
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,790
Even the provincial governor
have suffered because of them.

228
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:39,000
Why are you looking for trouble?

229
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,440
Just because

230
00:13:44,470 --> 00:13:45,280
they've coexisted with it,

231
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:47,030
does that prove they were right?

232
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:50,280
Why would I follow in their footsteps,

233
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,440
tolerating evil,

234
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,280
and ignoring the suffering
of common people?

235
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,470
Are you doing this for common people

236
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:00,760
or for Luo Shu?

237
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:04,470
I've made up my mind.

238
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,080
Say no more.

239
00:14:26,350 --> 00:14:27,960
You go to Pingyangwei right away,

240
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:30,030
asking for their assistance
in eliminating bandits.

241
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:30,670
Got it.

