[Bless and Protect People Extensively]

243
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:40,980
[Improve with Diligent Effort]

244
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:07,960
Mr. Chen,

245
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:08,880
do your job

246
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:10,520
