248
00:15:13,710 --> 00:15:14,280
If we can't

249
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,550
eradicate the White Ant this time,

250
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:16,640
the county yamen

251
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,230
will never be at peace again.

252
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:20,880
