253
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,350
Justice will triumph over evil.

254
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:25,640
Linfen is a civilized place.

255
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:27,320
I am the magistrate here.

256
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,080
If I cannot even

257
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,280
eradicate the White Ant,

258
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:30,440
a mere gang of bandits,

259
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,550
then how can I

260
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:33,080
face calling myself

261
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,710
the magistrate?

262
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:39,790
So stubborn.

263
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:25,710
Pingyangwei

264
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,710
