266
00:16:34,110 --> 00:16:35,280
It will be alright.

267
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,150
They're back.

268
00:16:46,640 --> 00:16:48,080
Victory!

269
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,880
Miss Luo,

270
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:53,520
