00:17:43,470 --> 00:17:44,400
Didn't expect that, huh?

276
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,760
I'm back.

277
00:17:46,430 --> 00:17:48,400
I, Qi Menglin,
the Deputy Commandant of Pingyangwei,

278
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:49,710
led the troops to eliminate bandits

279
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:52,110
and returned in triumph,

280
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:55,430
so I'm here to report back to you.

281
00:18:08,190 --> 00:18:09,000
Bring them up.

282
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,310
The White Ant has been
committing crimes for years,

283
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,310
extremely troublesome.

284
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:29,070
This operation was successful

285
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,800
thanks to you

